ell on my body and hydrates my sensitive skin with ease. When I step out of the shower after using this, I smell like I’ve just come back from a sweet beach vacation."}},"item_t4p9jj":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/forbes-logos-black-png-download-7.png","logo_width":76,"author":"Marie-Claire","content":"When you can’t make it to Marrakesh, you can check into the Shampoohotel anytime to escape with your skincare. Turn your bathroom into a hotel with this new brand that has four collections around iconic destinations: Miami, Marrakesh, Rio and Paris."}},"item_zy3xbG":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screen_Shot_2026-02-18_at_7.33.11_PM.png","logo_width":76,"author":"Elle","content":"Perfect if you’re dealing with damage or want a routine that doubles as sensory escape."}},"item_ymNNME":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ok_logo_black.png","logo_width":76,"author":"Elle","content":"Inspired by the beachside vibe of its namesake city, this leave-in conditioner is your shortcut to soft, hydrated, and effortlessly smooth hair. Infused with nourishing hyaluronic acid, the formula detangles and replenishes moisture to leave hair with a silky feel. This leave-in reduces frizz by up to 85%* in high humidity and is formulated for all hair types."}},"item_eEUFae":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screen_Shot_2026-02-18_at_7.34.58_PM.png","logo_width":76,"author":"Elle","content":"Bringing the charm of hotel amenities into the home, Shampoohotel offers a beauty range that combines sensorial fragrance, salon-quality formulas, and accessible pricing to elevate everyday routines."}},"item_U9qD7G":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/americansalonlogo.svg","logo_width":76,"author":"Elle","content":"Because that shower after a pool or beach day just hits different, especially on vacation. The decadent body products from this new travel-inspired hair and body brand are developed by in-house perfumers with scents inspired by iconic destinations: Paris (crisp and sophisticated), Miami (uplifting and bright), Marrakesh (sultry and striking), and Rio (warm and intoxicating). "}},"item_D3pdWY":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/rd-us-weekly-02-04-1.webp","logo_width":76,"author":"Elle","content":"The shampoo was luxuriously creamy and left my hair feeling clean but not stripped . . . the conditioner hydrated my waves really well without weighing them down. The fragrance of all of these products is heavenly, too; it’s this sunscreeny, summery, salty smell that I couldn’t stop opening the bottles to take a whiff of!”"}}},"block_order":["item_y6q8hi","item_t4p9jj","item_zy3xbG","item_ymNNME","item_eEUFae","item_U9qD7G","item_D3pdWY"],"custom_css":["blockquote {text-transform: none !important;}"],"settings":{"color_scheme":"scheme-2","title":"In the press","use_arrows_navigation":false,"show_quotation_mark":true,"quotation_tag":"h5","item_style":"logo","autoplay":true,"cycle_speed":6,"overlay_color":"#000000","overlay_opacity":20}}},"order":["main","image_with_text_overlay_h9pj6p","rich_text_4kUUG7","text_with_media_XXWpfP","text_with_media_GMEdVx","text_with_media_6R8jBX","image_with_text_overlay_Eqxpwf","rich_text_MzLLf4","video_JmWGqe","image_with_text_overlay_nVLXdH","dynamic_grid_9jTRk3","media_blocks_RKh3cD","scrolling_content_AykhDA","featured_collections_FGFwpG","image_with_text_overlay_BCx8p3","rich_text_QUPEX7","reading_text_TcTXWa","reading_text_jRXtmt","press_ixk7Yw"]}